    <note>Qin(1) Zhong [155] Anhui TZ, 154.7b; XCB, 267.10a-10b, 468.1b, 474.12b. Anhui TZ, 155.16a listes five undated Song Wuwei jun Qin jinshi--Jingwen, Jingshu, Jingfan, Jingyuan and Jingque (none included in dataset), who must be related to Zhong, but there are no other sources that list them or any other Qin sharing the same generational name (e.g. XCB and SHY indices). Wang(2) Zhidao's [1786] wife's (q.v.) mother, born Qin Shi (# 1 wife [of three] of her father) was also probably related to Zhong, most likely a daughter, which would explain the sudden emergence of the Wuwei Wang(2). CBD, 3, 1866.</note>
